    About this hotel

    Across the road from Tanger Beach on the Mediterranean Sea, this polished resort is 1 km from Tanger Ville railway station, and 4 km from museums in Dar-el-Makhzen, a 17th-century palace. …

    Warmly decorated rooms offer Wi-Fi access, flat-screen TVs, minibars and balconies; some provide pool or sea views. Upgraded rooms have sofabeds; suites add separate living rooms. Room service is available 24/7.

    Breakfast is free. Other amenities include a spa, a gym and an outdoor pool, plus meeting space. There are 3 restaurants (2 informal, 1 upscale), as well as a nightclub, a poolside cafe, and a contemporary bar featuring live music.
